<I c="Tutorial" i="tutorial" m="tutorials.tutorial" n="tutorial_EP14_NectarAgingAndNectarRack" s="347637">
  <T n="name">0xEDAEF37C<!--Nectar Aging & Nectar Rack--></T>
  <L n="slides">
    <U>
      <T n="image" p="InEP14\UI\Lessons\EP14_NectarAging_Slide1.png">2f7d0004:00000000:7c0d87fecc403608</T>
      <T n="text">0x83DE286D<!--How well-aged a Nectar is matters! The perfect way to age it more quickly and securely is to use a <b>Nectar Rack</b>! Store up to 13 bottles of Nectar in each <b>Nectar Rack</b>.\n\nYou can also age Nectar more quickly by storing it in a Basement. This will age it less quickly than a <b>Nectar Rack</b>, but more quickly than normal.--></T>
    </U>
    <U>
      <T n="image" p="InEP14\UI\Lessons\EP14_NectarAging_Slide2.png">2f7d0004:00000000:7c0d87fecc40360b</T>
      <T n="text">0xB2FB1156<!--When using a <b>Nectar Rack</b>: Once a Nectar is Finely Aged (the best aging it'll reach), the <b>Grab a Finely Aged Nectar Bottle</b> and <b>Collect All Finely Aged Nectar Bottles</b> interactions will become available on the object. These options will help you collect only the best and leave the rest of the Nectars in the <b>Nectar Rack</b> to age longer!--></T>
    </U>
    <U>
      <T n="image" p="InEP14\UI\Lessons\EP14_NectarAging_Slide3.png">2f7d0004:00000000:7c0d87fecc40360a</T>
      <T n="text">0x1AB23D43<!--Do you want to get super organized with Nectar? We do! Name your <b>Nectar Racks</b>. Select a <b>Nectar Rack</b> and choose the <b>Name</b> interaction. You can call it whatever you want. As an example, "Trash Nectar Storage." Then you can keep all of your Trash Nectar in it and never confuse it with the <i>obviously</i> less tasty Strawberry Nectar you keep in that <i>other</i> <b>Nectar Rack</b>.--></T>
    </U>
    <U>
      <T n="image" p="InEP14\UI\Lessons\EP14_NectarAging_Slide4.png">2f7d0004:00000000:7c0d87fecc40360d</T>
      <T n="text">0xECDA4DBB<!--Stack'n back'em! <b>Nectar Racks</b> are stackable and can be placed side-to-side and back-to-back. Arrange them any way you want to build an awesome Nectar aging room!--></T>
    </U>
    <U>
      <T n="image" p="InEP14\UI\Lessons\EP14_NectarAging_Slide5.png">2f7d0004:00000000:7c0d87fecc40360c</T>
      <T n="text">0xEFA427ED<!--But where can you find the <b>Nectar Rack</b>? The Rancher's Stackable Nectar Storage Rack can be found in Build Mode in the <b>Hobbies & Skills</b> or <b>Misc Decorations</b> categories.--></T>
    </U>
  </L>
